<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="estilos.css" />
    <title>Conecta Aí</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="cabecalho">
        <h1>Confere Aí</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#" class="cabecalho-link">Inicio</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h2>Descubra a verdade passando o mouse</h2>
        <section>
        <article class="cartao">
            <div class="cartao-interno">
                <div class="cartao-frente">
                    <img src="https://static.nationalgeographicbrasil.com/files/styles/image_3200/public/mm1012723121410486.jpg?w=1900&h=2849" alt="Pinguim" class="cartao-imagem">
                    <p>Pinguins conseguem voar como pássaros!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cartao-verso">
                    <img src="https://static.nationalgeographicbrasil.com/files/styles/image_3200/public/mm1012723121410486.jpg?w=1900&h=2849" alt="Pinguim"  class="cartao-imagem">
                    <p>Pinguins não voam, mas são excelentes nadadores.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
<article class="cartao">
            <div class="cartao-interno">
                <div class="cartao-frente">
                    <img src="https://static.nationalgeographicbrasil.com/files/styles/image_3200/public/mm1012723121410486.jpg?w=1900&h=2849" alt="Pinguim" class="cartao-imagem">
                    <p>Pinguins conseguem voar como pássaros!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cartao-verso">
                    <img src="https://static.nationalgeographicbrasil.com/files/styles/image_3200/public/mm1012723121410486.jpg?w=1900&h=2849" alt="Pinguim"  class="cartao-imagem">
                    <p>Pinguins não voam, mas são excelentes nadadores.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Projeto feito por Moni</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

  
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.cabecalho {
    padding: 15px 25px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #7e3e1c;
}

.cartao {
    width: 260px;
    height: 200px;
}

.cartao-imagem {
    width: 100%;
}

body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background-color: #f5f2f2;
}

main {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.cabecalho-link {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
}

h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 24px;
}

footer {
    background-color: #7e3e1c;
    padding: 15px 25px;
    color: #fff;
}

.cartao-interno {
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.8s;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
}

.cartao:hover .cartao-interno {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
}

.cartao-frente, .cartao-verso {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    backface-visibility: hidden;
}

.cartao-verso {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
}

section {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
}
